      <h2>Luxury Construction &amp; Renovation in Wailea</h2>
      <p>Wailea is Maui's premier resort destination — a master-planned community built around world-class golf courses, luxury hotels, and some of the most expensive real estate on the island. The Shops at Wailea, the Blue, Gold, and Emerald golf courses, and the flagship resort properties of the Grand Wailea, Four Seasons, and Andaz anchor a community where quality expectations are the highest on Maui.</p>

      <p>Construction and renovation work in Wailea demands a contractor who understands those expectations and delivers accordingly. Great General LLC has worked in Wailea's luxury residential market — on private estates, vacation villas, and high-end condominium units — and we approach every project with the attention to detail and quality of execution that this market requires.</p>

      <p>Wailea's properties are also among the most exposed to Maui's coastal environment. Many homes and villas sit on elevated lots with direct ocean views and direct trade wind exposure. Material selection, particularly for metalwork, exterior finishes, and hardware, requires more aggressive corrosion-resistance specifications than properties further from the coast. We've spec'd and installed enough metalwork in Wailea to know what holds up and what fails.</p>

      <h2>Residential Renovation in Wailea's Neighborhoods</h2>
      <p>Wailea's residential districts include some of Maui's most sought-after neighborhoods — Wailea Highlands above the resort corridor, Wailea Ekahi, Ekolu, and Elua condominium villages, the Palms at Wailea, Wailea Point, and the larger private estate lots in the Wailea-Makena corridor. Each of these communities has a distinct character and its own renovation requirements.</p>

      <p><strong>Wailea Highlands</strong> — The uphill residential community above Wailea's hotel strip consists primarily of larger single-family homes and estates with sweeping ocean views. Renovation projects here tend to be full or near-full home remodels, kitchen and bathroom renovations of considerable scale, and architectural metalwork projects including custom entry gates, deck railings, and lanai fencing. We've done substantial work in this neighborhood and understand its character.</p>

      <p><strong>Wailea Condominium Villages</strong> — The Ekahi, Ekolu, Elua, and surrounding communities are well-established condominium complexes with active HOAs and established renovation protocols. We work within these associations regularly — getting the necessary pre-approvals, coordinating with building management on noise and hours restrictions, and managing the logistics of renovation work in multi-unit buildings.</p>

      <p><strong>Wailea Point and Oceanfront Properties</strong> — The most exposed properties in Wailea, where direct salt spray and constant trade wind exposure require the most aggressive material specifications. Outdoor metalwork at these properties must be fabricated in 316L stainless or marine-grade aluminum — full stop. We do not cut corners on material specification at oceanfront properties, because the failure cost far exceeds the material cost.</p>

      <h2>Vacation Villa Renovation</h2>
      <p>Wailea's vacation rental market is concentrated in the upper tier — luxury villas and condominiums renting at significant nightly rates to discerning guests who have high expectations of fit and finish. Renovation work on vacation rental properties in Wailea needs to deliver both visual impact and functional durability under frequent occupancy.</p>

      <p>Common renovation scopes for Wailea vacation rentals include kitchen and bathroom upgrades to keep the property competitive in a luxury market, flooring replacement (moving from dated carpet to tile or LVP throughout), lanai improvements including railing replacement and shade structure additions, and layout modifications to improve flow and guest experience. We understand the rental calendar and the cost of vacancy — we schedule and execute these projects with that in mind.</p>

      <h2>Custom Metal Fabrication for Wailea Properties</h2>
      <p>Metal fabrication in Wailea's luxury market is both functional and architectural. Custom entry gates that make a statement, railings that provide safety while framing ocean views without obstruction, and architectural metalwork that integrates with a home's design language — these are common project types in Wailea that require skill in both design and fabrication.</p>

      <p>For Wailea properties, we work extensively with marine-grade aluminum and 316L stainless steel. These are the correct material choices for properties in Wailea's exposure environment, and they allow for clean, modern aesthetics that work well with the contemporary architecture typical of the area. We handle the full scope — design consultation, fabrication, post installation and concrete work, and finish metal installation — as a single scope without requiring the client to manage multiple contractors.</p>

      <h2>General Contracting in the Makena Corridor</h2>
      <p>South of Wailea, the Makena corridor — including Makena Surf, Polo Beach Club, Makena Landing, and the Makena Alanui estates — is even more exclusive, with some of the largest private estate lots on Maui's south shore. Construction and renovation projects here are often complex in scale and require careful coordination. We provide general contracting services throughout this corridor.</p>

      <h2>Services Available in Wailea</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Full-scope general contracting and project management for luxury residential projects</li>
        <li>Kitchen and bathroom remodels at luxury finish levels</li>
        <li>Interior framing and buildout for layout modifications and room additions</li>
        <li>Custom metal fabrication — oceanfront-grade gates, railings, and architectural metalwork</li>
        <li>Drywall, flooring, and custom carpentry throughout vacation rental and residential projects</li>
        <li>Maui County permit management for all project types</li>
        <li>HOA coordination for condominium renovation projects</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Why Wailea Property Owners Choose Great General</h2>
      <p>In a market where properties command top-tier pricing, the quality of renovation work directly affects property value and rental rates. Great General LLC brings the attention to detail, quality of execution, and direct owner involvement that Wailea's standards require. Noel runs every project personally — you're not handed off to a crew supervisor after the estimate. That level of engagement shows in the finished product.</p>

      <p>We're also honest about scope and budget. Wailea renovation projects can escalate quickly if not managed carefully. We define scope clearly upfront, flag potential issues early, and communicate proactively if anything changes during the project. No surprise invoices at the end.</p>

      <h2>Free On-Site Estimates in Wailea</h2>
      <p>Call or submit a request online and we'll schedule a free on-site estimate at your Wailea property. Whether it's a small bathroom renovation or a full estate remodel, we'll walk through the scope with you and give you a clear, written estimate at no charge.</p>
